lead_paragraph: Rohit Sharma and Virat Kohli maintained their prolific form with the bat to secure India's series-clinching 27-run win over Australia in the second Twenty20 match at the Melbourne Cricket Ground on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Rohit, Kohli Power India to Series Win in Melbourne
headline.main: Rohit, Kohli Power India to Series Win in Melbourne
